    <div class=\"top-image column1\">\n        \n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 begin-->\n    <div class=\"page-main-box\">\n        <div class=\"page-main\">\n            <div class=\"left-menu\">\n                <div class=\"head\">\n\n\n\n师资队伍</div>\n                <div class=\"head-line\"></div>\n                <ul>\n      <a href=\"../../szdw/jsdw.htm\" title=\"教师队伍\"><li class=\"on\">教师队伍</li></a>\n    <a href=\"../../szdw/bssds1.htm\" title=\"博士生导师\"><li>博士生导师</li></a>\n    <a href=\"../../szdw/czxgzdjs.htm\" title=\"曾在系工作的教师\"><li>曾在系工作的教师</li></a>\n</ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"right-main-box\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;height:52px;\"></div>\n                <div class=\"right-main\">\n                    <div class=\"right-map\">\n                        \n\n\n\n<div class=\"left\">\n正高级\n</div>\n\n\n                        <div class=\"right\">\n    当前位置：\n                        <a href=\"../../index.htm\" style=\"color:#000;\">首页</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jsdw.htm\" style=\"color:#000;\">师资队伍</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jsdw.htm\" style=\"color:#000;\">教师队伍</a>\n</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <!--这里放主体显示部分-->\n                    <div class=\"szdw-detail right-column-box\">\n                        \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/photoswipe.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/klass.min.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n         <div id=\"vsb_content desc\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<div class=\"basic-box\">\n            \n <div class=\"timg\">\n  <img src=\"/__local/9/A5/C4/EF0D7C8921A0224233D6BCA93A1_1EE31066_6F2C.jpg?e=.jpg\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/9A5C4EF0D7C8921A0224233D6BCA93A1/1EE31066/6F2C?e=.jpg\" vheight=\"\" vwidth=\"\" orisrc=\"/__local/9/A5/C4/EF0D7C8921A0224233D6BCA93A1_1EE31066_6F2C.jpg?e=.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\"> \n </div>\n <div class=\"tbasic\">\n               \n  <div class=\"tname\">\n   王学武\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"tposition\">\n   教授\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n  <div class=\"tcontent\">\n                  \n   <p>博士、教授</p>\n   <p>电话：010-62784717　+86-10-6278 4717</p>\n   <p>传真：010-62782658　+86-10-6278 2658</p>\n   <p>邮箱：wangxuewu@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"right-column-menu tright-column-menu list-paddingleft-2\">\n \n <li class=\"on\"><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   教育背景\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   工作经历\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   教学工作\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   研究领域\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   研究概况\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   学术成果\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   学术兼职\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   奖励与荣誉\n  </div><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n  <div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n <li><p><br></p></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<div class=\"tli-content jy-background tli-content-on\">\n <p>● 1997.09 - 2005.06　清华大学工程物理系　核技术及应用专业　工学博士</p>\n <p>● 1993.09 - 1997.07　清华大学工程物理系　工程物理专业　工学学士</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content job-record tli-content-\">\n <p>● 2016.06 - 至今　　　清华大学工程物理系　教授　</p>\n <p>● 2013.12 - 2016.06　清华大学工程物理系　研究员</p>\n <p>● 2009.11 - 2016.06　清华大学工程物理系　副系主任</p>\n <p>● 2007.12 - 2013.12　清华大学工程物理系　副研究员</p>\n <p>● 2002.12 - 2007.12　清华大学工程物理系　讲师</p>\n <p>● 1998.08 - 2002.12　清华大学工程物理系　助教</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content jx-work tli-content-\">\n <p>● 培养已毕业工学博士1名，在读工学博士8名；</p>\n <p>● 培养已毕业工学硕士3名；</p>\n <p>● 培养已毕业工程硕士3名。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content yj-part tli-content-\">\n <p>● 学科方向：核技术及应用。</p>\n <p>● 主要研究方向包括辐射成像技术及应用，中子源、中子谱仪技术及应用等。</p>\n <p>● 主要研究课题包括高能X 射线双能成像物质识别方法及其技术应用研究，低能X 射线成像技术及其应用研究，宇宙线缪子成像方法、关键技术研究及实验平台研制，清华大学微型脉冲强子源研究与建设，中子谱仪技术、中子探测器技术及其应用研究等。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content yj-basic tli-content-\">\n <p>● 核技术及其应用（11322548）　国家自然科学基金委优秀青年基金　2014.01-2016.12　负责人</p>\n <p>● 长脉冲中子源慢化器中子学性能理论分析与实验测量（11275106）　国家自然科学基金委面上基金　2013.01-2016.12　负责人</p>\n <p>● 中子散射装置数据获取电子学系统研发　中物院中子物理学重点实验室基金　2012.11-2013.12　负责人</p>\n <p>● 宇宙线缪子成像特殊对象检测关键技术研究　清华大学自主科研　2011.11-2014.12　负责人</p>\n <p>● 宇宙线缪子成像关键物理与技术问题研究(11035002)　国家自然科学基金委重点基金　2011.01-2014.12　骨干</p>\n <p>● 微型脉冲强子源　985二期　2009.06-2013.12　负责人</p>\n <p>● 科技新星（A类）　北京市科委 　2009.01-2010.12　负责人</p>\n <p>● 高能X射线多能谱成像法识别物质的关键物理与技术问题研究（10705018）　国家自然科学基金委青年基金　2008.01-2010.12　负责人</p>\n <p>● 增强型移动式双能集装箱/车辆检查系统总体设计及相关核心技术研究　同方威视　2006.09-2007.07　负责人</p>\n <p>● 移动式双能集装箱/车辆检查系统总体设计及相关核心技术研究　同方威视　2005.09-2006.12 　负责人</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content xs-result tli-content-\">\n <p>● Zhujun Fang, Yigang Yang, Yulan Li, Zhi Zhang, and Xuewu Wang. Research on a Neutron Detector with a Boron-Lined Honeycomb Neutron Converter. IEEE TRANSACTIONS ON NUCLEAR SCIENCE, VOL. 64, NO. 4, APRIL 2017, 1048-1055.</p>\n <p>● Zhujun Fang, Yigang Yang, Yulan Li, and Xuewu Wang. Working Gas Selection of the Honeycomb Converter-Based Neutron Detector. IEEE TRANSACTIONS ON NUCLEAR SCIENCE, VOL. 64, NO. 7, JULY 2017, 1683-1688.</p>\n <p>● Huarui Wu, Boris Khaykovich, Xuewu Wang, Daniel S. Hussey. Wolter mirrors for neutron imaging. Physics Procedia. Vol. 88, 2017, 184 – 189.</p>\n <p>● Guang-Rui Li, Shu-Xin Zheng,Hong-Juan Yao, Xia-Ling Guan, Xue-Wu Wang,Wen-Hui Huang. Design of a compact ring for proton radiation Applications. Chinese Physics C Vol. 41, No. 1 (2017).</p>\n <p>● X Wang, CK Loong, X Guan, etc. Recent Progress of the Compact Pulsed Hadron Source Project and Related Activities at Tsinghua University. Physics Procedia. Vol. 60, 2014, 97 – 100.</p>\n <p>● X. Wang, Q. Xing, C-K. Loong, etc. Delivery of 3-MeV Proton and Neutron Beams at CPHS: A Status Report on Accelerator and Neutron Activities at Tsinghua University. Physics Procedia. Physics Procedia. Vol. 60, 2014, 186–192.</p>\n <p>● T.C. Huang, H. Gong, B.B. Shao, X.W. Wang*, etc. Development of 3He LPSDs and read-out system for the SANS spectrometer at CPHS. NUCL INSTRUM METH A. Vol. 735, 21 Jan 2014, Pages 374–378.</p>\n <p>● Cai Chen, Yigang Yang ; Shounuo Zhu ; Weiqi HuangHui Gong, Xuewu Wang*, etc. Study of boron-lined straw-tube detector array for neutron scattering measurement, 2012 IEEE NSS/MIC, 176-9.</p>\n <p>● C. Chen, Gong, H. ; Yang, Y. ; Zhu, S., Huang, T., Wang, Y., Xuewu Wang*, etc. Realization and Test of Position Sensitive Boron Coated Straw-Tube, 2013 IEEE NSS/MIC.</p>\n <p>● Zhong Bin, Yu Ganglin, Wang Xuewu, Wang Kan. Comparisons on thin and thick neutron target for low energy proton beam, Int. Conf. Phys. React., PHYSOR: Adv. React. Phys., vol. 3, 2012, 2440-2449.</p>\n <p>● C. -K. Loong, Jie Wei, Xialing Guan, Xuewu Wang. The Impact on Science and Technology of University-Based, Accelerator-Driven, Compact Neutron and Proton Sources: A Case in Point in China. Physics Procedia. Volume 26, 2012, Pages 8–18.</p>\n <p>● Xuewu Wang, Ming Zeng, Zhi Zeng, etc. The cosmic ray muon tomography facility based on large scale MRPC detectors. NUCL INSTRUM METH A. Vol. 784, 1 Jun 2015, Pages 390–393.</p>\n <p>● Xuewu Wang, Jianping Cheng, Ming Zeng, etc. Preliminary research on performance evaluation and TUCCI model for muon tomography. 2013 IEEE NSS/MIC.</p>\n <p>● Xuewu Wang, Jianping Cheng, Yi Wang, etc. Design and construction of muon tomography facility based on MRPC detector for high-Z materials detection. 2012 IEEE NSS/MIC. 83-5.</p>\n <p>● Wang Xue-Wu, Li Jian-Min, Kang Ke-Jun, etc. Material discrimination by high-energy X-ray dual-energy imaging. High Energy Physics and Nuclear Physics- Chinese Edition, vol. 31, issue 11, Nov 2007, 1076-1081.</p>\n <p>● Chen Zhiqiang, Wang Xuewu. Cargo X-ray Imaging Technology for Material Discrimination. Port Technology International. May. 2006, 30th ed., 163-165.</p>\n <p>● 李清华, 李荐民, 王学武, 等. 重叠材料的高能X射线双能成像识别技术, 清华大学学报（自然科学版）, 2008, Vol.48, No. 8, 1256-9.</p>\n <p>● 李清华, 王学武, 李荐民, 等. 高能X射线双能成像系统中多能谱探测器研究. 核电子学与探测技术, 2008, Vol.28, No.4, 821-5.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content xs-job tli-content-\">\n <p>● 2018.05-至今　　　中国核学会副秘书长，青年工作委员会主任委员；</p>\n <p>● 2015.09-2018.05　中国核学会青年工作委员会副主任委员；</p>\n <p>● 2014.07-至今　　　中国核学会核测试与分析分会副理事长；</p>\n <p>● 2013.06-至今　　　中国物理学会中子散射专业委员会委员；</p>\n <p>● 2011.06-至今　　　中国散裂中子源工程科学技术委员会委员；</p>\n <p>● 2010.09-至今　　　加速器驱动的小型中子源国际联盟（UCANS）委员会。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tli-content reward tli-content-\">\n <p>● 2014年　“核技术及应用”获“国家优秀青年科学基金”资助;</p>\n <p>● 2013年　“清华大学辐射成像创新团队”获“国家科学技术进步奖（创新团队）”（13/15）；</p>\n <p>● 2008年　“液体安全检查系统”获“信息产业重大技术发明奖”（7/12）；</p>\n <p>● 2008年　　获“北京市科技新星计划（A类）”资助；</p>\n <p>● 2005年　“本科以上定向核专业人才培养输送模式与实践”获“北京市教育教学成果（高等教育）一等奖” （3/5）。</p>\n</div>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n    \n    <script>\n    $(function() {\n        var str = $('.page-main-box .right-main-box .right-main .szdw-detail .basic-box').html().replace(/&nbsp;/ig, '');\n        $('.page-main-box .right-main-box .right-main .szdw-detail .basic-box').html(str);\n    })\n    </script>\n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    <div class=\"links-box\">\n        <div class=\"links\">\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:20px;\"></div>\n            <div class=\"model-title\">\n                <div class=\"model\">常用链接</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"model-block\"></div>\n            <ul>\n      <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74493)\"><li>清华大学</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://news.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74494)\"><li>清华新闻网</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://tsinghua.cn.libguides.com/c.php?g=915369\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74495)\"><li>图书馆－核学科</li></a>\n</ul>\n            <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:41px;\"></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"copy-right-box\">\n        <div style=\"width:100%;height:26px;\"></div>\n        <ul>\n            <script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/mp4video.js\"></script>\n<li>地址：清华大学工程物理系（刘卿楼）</li> \n<li>邮编：100084</li> \n<li>电话：010-62785727</li> \n<li>邮箱：gwbgs@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div style=\"width:100%;height:10px;\"></di